                                                            <field name="LANG">markdown</field>
                                                            <field name="CODE"># LinkedIn API Setup

1. **Get API Access**: 
   - Create LinkedIn Developer account
   - Create new app at https://www.linkedin.com/developers/apps
   - Get client credentials

2. **Authentication**: 
   - Implement OAuth 2.0 flow
   - Get access token for API calls
   - Replace 'YOUR_LINKEDIN_TOKEN' in code

3. **API Limits**: 
   - Free tier: 100 API calls/day
   - Rate limits apply per endpoint
   - Cache responses when possible

4. **Required Permissions**:
   - r_liteprofile (basic profile)
   - r_organization_social (company data)
   - w_member_social (posting)</field>
